Step 17: Resolve Manifest Error

Open:
vi pom.xml
```
Add before `</project>`:

```xml
<build>
  <plugins>

    <plugin>
      <artifactId>maven-jar-plugin</artifactId>
      <version>3.1.0</version>

      <configuration>
        <archive>
          <manifest>
            <addClasspath>true</addClasspath>
            <mainClass>com.example.App</mainClass>
          </manifest>
        </archive>
      </configuration>

    </plugin>

  </plugins>
</build>
```

Save file.

